1. When the user is asked for permission to allow location
    a. If Allow Once is clicked
         Every time when the user has relaunched the app the allow location must be prompted.
    b. If Allow Always is clicked
        Nothing must be done. But the app must update the weather data.
    c. If Don't Allow is clicked.
        Everytime popup a dialogue to allow location.
2. Check the data is coming for the correct location or know.
3. Check if the city is not coming in data, set the latitude and longitude instead.
4. All 16 days forecasts are available or not.
5. Refresh button must work.
